-- James Cameron Company Forms 3D Movie Venture in China’s Tianjin
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2012-08-08T01:07:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-08/james-cameron-company-forms-3d-movie-venture-in-china-s-tianjin.html
James Cameron ’s Cameron Pace Group
formed a venture in the northern Chinese city of Tianjin to
develop 3D film equipment and provide training for making the
movies, the official Xinhua News Agency reported.  The venture agreement was signed by Cameron Pace Group’s
co-chairmen Cameron and Vince Pace, along with Tianjin Hitech
Holding Group Chairman Gong Jing and Tianjin North Film Group
Chairman Wang Dafang, according to Xinhua. The report did give
financial or ownership details about the venture.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
John Liu at 
 jliu42@bloomberg.net  